import React from 'react'; const Form = ({newSpacecraft, setNewSpacecraft}) => { const handleChange = e => { setNewSpacecraft({ ...newSpacecraft, [e.target.name]: e.target.value }) } let { name, type, activity, origin, tripulation, combustible, state, weight } = newSpacecraft const handleSubmit = () => { tripulation = parseInt(tripulation, 10); //validate the data if(name === '' || type === '' || activity === '' || origin === '' || tripulation < 0 || combustible === '' || state === '' || weight ==='' ) { alert('Todos los campos son oblogatorios') return } //query const requestInit = { method: 'POST', headers: {'Content-Type': 'application/json'}, body: JSON.stringify(newSpacecraft) } fetch('http://localhost:8080/api/v1/spacecraft', requestInit) .then(res => res.json()) .then(res => console.log(res)) // restarting newSpacecraftState setNewSpacecraft({ name: '', activity: '', origin: '', tripulation: 0, combustible: '', state: '', weight: '', burden: '', thrust: '', height: '', power: '', objectOfStudy: '', inOrbit: '', speed: '', mission: '' }) } return (
); } export default Form;
